name: TWO x TWO
description: **TWO x TWO for AIDS and Art** is the contemporary art auction benefiting amfAR, The Foundation for AIDS Research, and the Dallas Museum of Art, held annually at the Rachofsky House in Dallas, Texas. Artsy hosted the online premiere of the OWN it NOW auction October 18 to 24. Online bidding for the OWN it NOW auction on Artsy has closed. For more information, please visit the full TWO x TWO catalogue at twoxtwo.org/catalogue or contact Trish Ireland at trish@rachofskyhouse.org.
